<section class="av_textblock_section "  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  '   itemprop="text" ><p><span class="hotkey-layer "><span class="hotkey-layer preview-overlay is-preview-sidebar-visible">Create high quality and sustainable crops for the future begins with crop varieties that produce the desired traits specific to the environments where they are grown.The plant breeding cluster will focus on developing Artificial Intelligence tools to help plant breeders develop the next generation of high yielding, high-quality, nutritious, and flavorful varieties of vegetables, fruit and nut cropsusing data-driven, molecular breeding approaches.</span></span></p>
</div></section></div><div class="flex_column av_one_fifth  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-5  el_after_av_three_fifth  avia-builder-el-last  " style='border-radius:0px; '></div>

