<p><span class="hotkey-layer "><span class="hotkey-layer preview-overlay is-preview-sidebar-visible">The AIFS molecular breeding team will create solutions in two areas:</span></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span class="hotkey-layer "><span class="hotkey-layer preview-overlay is-preview-sidebar-visible">Use Artificial Intelligence to extract data from imagesof growing plants in the field and fruits and vegetables in storage to reduce the labor and time costs of measuring breeding materials, and expand the size of breeding experiments.</span></span></li>
<li><span class="hotkey-layer "><span class="hotkey-layer preview-overlay is-preview-sidebar-visible">UseArtificial Intelligence to help breeders to run more efficient and targeted breeding programs that can simultaneously improve crops in multiple ways while maintaining flexibility to meet future challenges.</span></span></li>
</ul>
